      "beast_baseline": "i'm a bit confused why you keep using those weird analogies. anyway, i'll get a soil test kit. if it turns out the pH is actually okay and it really is just a nutrient thing, what kind of fertilizer should i look for? should i just get one that says 'acid loving plants' or is there something specific for iron?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
